PET/CT (February 2025): Left breast lesion (1.7 × 1.5 cm) with low FDG uptake (maximum standardized uptake value [SUVmax] 2.0), metabolically inactive axillary lymphadenopathy, and an incidental left thyroid lesion (4.0 × 3.8 cm, SUVmax 3.4) (
Fig. 1
).

